(ns cogito.subs
  (:require [re-frame.core :as rf]))

(rf/reg-sub
 :current-prompt
 (fn [db]
   (:current-prompt db)))

(rf/reg-sub
 :turns
 (fn [db]
   (:turns db)))

(rf/reg-sub
 :loading?
 (fn [db]
   (:loading? db)))

(rf/reg-sub
 :authenticated?
 (fn [db]
   (:authenticated? db)))

(rf/reg-sub
 :user
 (fn [db]
   (:user db)))

(rf/reg-sub
 :pending-client-selection?
 (fn [db]
   (:pending-client-selection? db)))

(rf/reg-sub
 :available-clients
 (fn [db]
   (:available-clients db)))

(rf/reg-sub
 :selecting-client?
 (fn [db]
   (:selecting-client? db)))

(rf/reg-sub
 :client-selection-error
 (fn [db]
   (:client-selection-error db)))

(rf/reg-sub
 :logging-out?
 (fn [db]
   (:logging-out? db)))

(rf/reg-sub
 :current-alternative-index
 (fn [db [_ turn-id]]
   (get-in db [:alternative-indices turn-id] 0)))

(rf/reg-sub
 :workbench/active-tab
 (fn [db]
   (get db :workbench/active-tab :conversation)))
